name: FAutomationWorkerFindWorkersResponse
doc: Implements a message that is sent in response to FAutomationWorkerFindWorkers.

DeviceName: Holds the name of the device that the worker is running on.
InstanceName: Holds the name of the worker's application instance.
Platform: Holds the name of the platform that the worker is running on.
OSVersionName: Holds the name of the operating system version.
ModelName: Holds the name of the device model.
GPUName: Holds the name of the GPU.
CPUModelName: Holds the name of the CPU model.
RAMInGB: Holds the amount of RAM this device has in gigabytes.
RenderModeName: Holds the name of the current render mode.
SessionId: Holds the worker's application session identifier.
RHIName: Holds the name of the current RHI.
